heading: Bigg Boss 15 Episode 95 Written Update
summary:
On the 95th episode of Bigg Boss 15, Rakhi Sawant and Devoleena made many
revelations. The show will soon enter its final week.

heading: Omicron symptoms not as 'mild', here's what experts say
summary:
While there’s a general consensus that an infection caused by Omicron is
milder than Delta variant, experts say even minor symptoms can feel
“uncomfortable” and may develop into “long Covid”.

heading: Yash looks deadly in new poster of KGF Chapter 2. Seen yet?
summary:
On January 8, Kannada actor Yash is celebrating his birthday. As a gift, the
makers of KGF: Chapter 2 released a special poster.

heading: Pujara reminds me of Hashim Amla, it's a blessing to have him: Sunil Gavaskar
summary:
Sunil Gavaskar said that Cheteshwar Pujara reminds him of former South Africa
opener Hashim Amla. Gavaskar further added that players with Pujara's
temperament are a blessing to the dressing room.

heading: Google faces probe in India after news publishers complain of unfair conditions
summary:
Internet giant Google is facing a probe in India following allegations from
news publishers, saying its initial view was that the tech giant had broken
some antitrust laws.

heading: Petrol, Diesel prices today: Fuel rates kept unchanged on January 8 | Check latest rates
summary:
The prices of petrol and diesel have been kept unchanged across the country
on Saturday, January 8, 2022. Check the latest city-wise rates here.

heading: Trisha tests positive for Covid-19, currently in isolation
summary:
On January 7, Trisha took to social media to inform her fans that she had
tested positive for Covid-19 before New Year. She also added that she is
recovering.

heading: Naomi Osaka pulls out of Melbourne tournament semifinal
summary:
Defending Australian Open champion Naomi Osaka has withdrawn from her
semifinal match at a WTA tournament in Melbourne with an abdominal injury.

heading: 83 box office collection Day 15
summary:
Ranveer Singh's 83 is soon going to enter the Rs 100 crore club in India. The
film released on December 24.

heading: India logs 1.41 lakh new Covid-19 cases in 24 hours, Omicron tally reaches 3,071
summary:
India registered 1,41,986 new Covid-19 cases in the last 24 hours, 21.3 per
cent higher than yesterday.

heading: In report to Centre, Bathinda SSP blames Ferozepur SSP on PM's security breach in Punjab
summary:
In Punjab government's report to the Centre, Bathinda senior superintendent
of police has blamed his Ferozepur counterpart for the lapse in security of
PM Modi on the flyover.

heading: Omicron surge pushes US Covid hospitalisations toward record high
summary:
Hospitalisations have increased steadily since late December as Omicron
quickly overtook Delta as the dominant coronavirus variant in the US.
